	Section 10.3(a)(iv) of the Reseller Agreement permits Shift4 to terminate the Reseller Agreement at any time, with or without cause, upon thirty (30) days’ prior written notice. Please accept this letter as Shift4’s notice that it is exercising its termination right under Section 10.3(a)(iv). Accordingly, and consistent with Section 10.7 of the Reseller Agreement, Shift4 will submit final invoices to CardConnect for (a) services rendered through the date of termination; and (b) any early termination fees due under the Reseller Agreement or compensation due to Shift4 for its purchase of MID(s) in its sole discretion. Shift4 demands payment of all such amounts in a timely manner.
